Iran’s President Ahmadinejad to Run Oil Ministry After Minister Dismissed

-- B y   L a d a n e   N a s s e r i
-- 
2011-05-15T19:08:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/iran-s-president-ahmadinejad-to-run-oil-ministry-after-minister-dismissed.html
Iran President Mahmoud Ahmadinejad
said he will oversee the country’s oil ministry following the
dismissal yesterday of Oil Minister Masoud Mir-Kazemi. The
president spoke in an interview on state television late
tonight.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladane Nasseri in Tehran at 
